 About Us: 
We are passionate about creating a shopping experience that customers will love. If you are an experienced and innovative L&D leader who is passionate about high-quality, innovative, and meaningful development experiences that drive measurable results with far-reaching impact, then we want to hear from you.
 
 The Role: 
We are looking for a leader with an experience strategizing and executing on large-scale projects in the L&D space as well as experience implementing digital L&D products. In this position, you will be single threaded owner for all L&D products, managing the entire product lifecycle from strategic planning to tactical execution. This position requires a solid technical background. You will need a high degree of ownership, strong business acumen, excellent communication and influencing skills, and experience with learning technologies. You thrive in a fast-paced environment and are great at developing product vision and strategy by working backward from the customer and defining / driving overall product strategies and roadmaps.
 
